15
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,240
Oh, my goodness.

16
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,719
Pack your things up

17
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:53,400
and go back to your own home now.

18
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:56,439
