34
00:03:43,919 --> 00:03:44,800
Alright, thank you.

35
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:45,719
You're welcome.

36
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:49,919
Hey.

37
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,560
Isn't she the daughter-in-law

38
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,039
of the Wang family?

39
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,240
That's her.

40
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:56,759
Did she really beat Chuanjia?

41
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,199
Yes, it was her.

42
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,560
I saw it with my own eyes.

43
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,080
Blimey, that was scary.

44
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,560
