101
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:49,560
I...

102
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,639
I need to hang up now.

103
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:52,920
I'll call you later.

104
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,759
Wan...

105
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:57,839
You...

106
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,079
