107
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,920
Chuanjia.

108
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,199
What fresh news

109
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,720
in Wan Village

110
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:12,279
that someone got beaten badly by a newly-wed

111
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:14,319
on a big day.

112
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:16,000
It must be written into the annals of the village.

113
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:18,120
What are you saying?

114
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,199
Stop being sarcastic.

115
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:20,199
Exactly.

116
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,160
The net on the head

117
00:06:27,519 --> 00:06:28,959
is such an annoyance to my gorgeousness.

118
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:34,800
She's really something.

119
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,480
A dainty

120
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,519
yet ruthless woman.

121
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,279
Fine. Just wait and see.

122
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:47,560
Xingfu, Qinglai is looking for you.

123
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,199
Qinglai, she's back.

124
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,000
Xingfu.

125
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,560
Where have you gone?

126
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:57,160
I was looking for you.

127
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,680
I went to the health center

128
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,279
and I spotted Wan Chuanjia.

129
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:02,199
I thought

130
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:03,680
he was taken to the county hospital.

131
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,160
No.

132
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:06,279
A nurse told me

133
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,680
