174
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,759
but we owe them an apology.

175
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:32,800
Tomorrow, you should bring Xingfu along

176
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,560
to pay a call on Mr. Wan

177
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:36,319
and apologize to them.

178
00:08:36,319 --> 00:08:37,079
Then,

179
00:08:37,680 --> 00:08:38,680
