180
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,320
Xingfu.

181
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,240
Did you hear that?

182
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,840
We'll visit Mr. Wan tomorrow

183
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,720
and eat the humble pie.

184
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,399
And everything will be over.

185
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,519
Xingfu.

186
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:57,600
Alright.

187
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:05,919
(Come and eat.)

188
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,840
(Xiuyu.)

189
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,759
(-Coming.)
(-Qingzhi, come and eat.)

190
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:18,960
Dad.

191
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:21,519
You should have been there.

192
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,759
Chuanjia was bleeding heavily

193
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,879
when he was taken

194
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:26,360
to the health center.

195
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:28,799
