197
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,120
They should have beaten you harder.

198
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,000
Only those youngsters would play pranks
at the bridal chamber ritual,

199
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,639
