208
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,159
to be hit by the woman who just got married.

209
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:51,320
Okay, I got it.

210
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,799
No worries.

211
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,720
I'll go to her with a few people tomorrow.

212
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:56,320
What are you going to do?

213
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:57,960
I'm going to see her at Wang's house.

214
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,240
I can't let it slide.

215
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,000
Don't you dare.

216
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,200
You were hit by her

217
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,159
in such a situation.

218
00:10:02,159 --> 00:10:02,960
Yet, you still want to make a big scene

219
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,799
by going to her house to see her.

220
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:05,000
Everyone will know eventually.

221
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,639
Don't you think it was embarrassing enough?

222
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:07,679
I know it was embarrassing.

223
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:08,559
That's why I'm thinking of...

224
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,159
Shut up!

225
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:13,159
You're already in your thirties.

226
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,840
Although you're not a member of the party,

227
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,440
you're a member of the Wan Village Committee.

228
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,279
You're always acting ignorantly.

229
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:22,879
I wouldn't dare let you inherit the business
of the Wanjia Group.

230
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,919
Answer your phone call.

231
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,240
Mind your own business.

232
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,039
Chuanmei.

233
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:34,720
Dad.

234
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,600
Chuanmei.

235
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,360
How have you been lately?

236
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,240
How is your health condition?

237
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,559
I've not been doing good.

238
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,360
Your brother has been making me angry.

239
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,120
I'm reprimanding him now.

240
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,559
Don't listen to dad spouting nonsense.

241
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:46,080
He's about to get himself a new wife.

242
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:48,240
Dad.

243
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,519
Chuanmei.

244
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,240
Don't get angry because of him.

245
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,879
I'm not angry

246
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,039
after hearing your voice.

247
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,320
Come back soon

248
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,159
to supervise him on my behalf.

249
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:58,200
When are you coming back?

250
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:00,799
After I'm done with my work.

251
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:03,720
Go ahead and carry on with your work.

252
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,919
