269
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,120
is making us worried.

270
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,240
I think she's quite good.

271
00:13:49,279 --> 00:13:51,039
She dares to speak up and stand up for others.

272
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,879
She's not a coward.

273
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,559
There's nothing good
about standing up for others.

274
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,440
As the saying goes,

275
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,679
the one who stands up first will be bullied.

276
00:14:00,159 --> 00:14:00,960
Why is it so?

277
00:14:01,919 --> 00:14:03,240
Because he's seeking trouble.

278
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,080
That's much better than being a coward.

279
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:07,279
The three men of the Wang family

280
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:08,440
are all upright.

281
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,320
But when there's an issue,

282
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,679
they will chicken out.

283
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:12,000
How useless.

284
00:14:12,879 --> 00:14:14,240
Now I understand

285
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:16,799
that you want our daughter-in-law
to be on your side.

286
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:18,879
You're right.

287
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,159
So what?

288
00:14:37,639 --> 00:14:38,399
Xingfu.

289
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,279
Xingfu.

290
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:49,559
Why did you wake up?

291
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,480
Why are you sitting here?

292
00:15:02,919 --> 00:15:04,200
Haven't you been sleeping?

293
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,360
What are you thinking about?

294
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,200
I thought that I'd understood it.

295
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,759
But after thinking about it a couple of times,
I think

296
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:17,519
that it's not reasonable

297
00:15:17,519 --> 00:15:18,759
for us to apologize to Wan Chuanjia

298
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:21,440
when he was the one

299
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,440
who bullied my sister first.

300
00:15:27,879 --> 00:15:29,720
Do you all celebrate a marriage like that here?

301
00:15:33,559 --> 00:15:34,360
Xingfu.

302
00:15:36,759 --> 00:15:38,000
Our family

303
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,519
are small potatoes and have no power

304
00:15:41,559 --> 00:15:42,519
in the Wan Village.

305
00:15:43,279 --> 00:15:44,080
My parents

306
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:46,039
wouldn't dare offend
the superiors in the village.

307
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,399
They're afraid that your life won't be peaceful
in the future.

308
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:51,120
Do bear with it.

309
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:54,960
Moreover,

310
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:58,039
you've hit him on his head.

311
00:16:04,039 --> 00:16:04,799
You're right.

312
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,879
After all, I hit him on his head.

313
00:16:09,279 --> 00:16:11,039
I should go and apologize to him.

314
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,120
Xingfu.

315
00:16:21,879 --> 00:16:23,840
I can see

316
