320
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:39,750
okay?

321
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,300
Xingfu, regardless of anything,

322
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:03,820
Mr. Wan is the elder.

323
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:05,700
