324
00:17:06,470 --> 00:17:07,660
Don't act inappropriately.

325
00:17:08,870 --> 00:17:09,990
Say more positive things.

326
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:11,470
Do you get it?

327
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:14,710
Dad and Mom, I got it.

328
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:16,430
Go then.

329
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:17,750
We'll make a move then.

330
00:17:22,140 --> 00:17:23,140
Xiuyu.

331
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:24,470
Stop learning.

332
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:26,910
None of the guests eat well yesterday.

333
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:29,430
I'm going to sort out the candies and cigarettes.

334
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:31,820
After I'm done, send them to each house
with your brother.

335
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:35,540
I'm not going.

336
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:37,540
The one who is in the wrong
should make up for the mistake.

337
00:17:37,540 --> 00:17:38,750
It doesn't make sense for me to go.

338
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,750
Is it so hard for you to send the candies?

339
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:42,620
Does it trouble you a lot?

340
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:43,270
I'm busy.

341
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:44,990
I still have to read lots of books.

342
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:49,380
You're just a woman.

343
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:50,750
It's useless for you to study every day.

344
00:17:51,380 --> 00:17:53,140
I want to study accounting.

345
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:54,270
You're not capable enough

346
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:55,510
to study accounting.

347
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:56,470
You have the surname "Wang",

348
00:17:56,780 --> 00:17:57,620
not "Wan".

349
00:17:58,340 --> 00:17:59,540
I can't believe you're thinking
of climbing the social ladder.

350
00:17:59,950 --> 00:18:01,060
Just find someone to get married to.

351
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:02,140
That's much better than anything else.

352
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:03,140
Hurry up and go.

353
00:18:07,190 --> 00:18:07,860
You go, too.

354
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:15,990
Go and get a bun.

355
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:24,670
The kid has already grown up,

356
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:25,710
but he's not eating at the table.

357
00:18:25,710 --> 00:18:27,710
You adults didn't set rules for him either.

358
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:30,140
His mom failed to teach him properly.

359
00:18:30,430 --> 00:18:31,270
If she doesn't feed him like this,

360
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:32,270
what should we do if he's not willing to eat?

361
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:33,510
Are you not going to do anything about it?

362
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:35,300
You failed to set a good example for him.

363
00:18:36,910 --> 00:18:38,140
You always check your phone while eating.

364
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:39,670
Always.

365
00:18:39,910 --> 00:18:41,060
That's why the kid won't behave well.

366
00:18:41,990 --> 00:18:43,340
I learned this from you.

367
00:18:43,340 --> 00:18:44,620
Are you solely focusing on eating?

368
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,270
You're also holding different things.

369
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:48,300
We're checking out different things.

370
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:50,620
The county superior is coming to inspect

371
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:51,950
