producing healthcare products tomorrow.

372
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:53,710
I have to get prepared.

373
00:18:53,910 --> 00:18:54,780
You can't possibly take part in it

374
00:18:54,780 --> 00:18:55,820
in such a condition.

375
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:00,270
If that's the case,

376
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:02,430
I'll tell the superior tomorrow

377
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:05,100
that when I went to the construction site
for inspection earlier,

378
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:06,580
I was hit on the head

379
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:07,710
by falling rocks on the mountain.

380
00:19:07,710 --> 00:19:08,950
The superiors prefer this kind of reason.

381
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:10,030
Go away.

382
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:13,140
You're not exactly cultured

383
00:19:13,910 --> 00:19:15,620
but you always have some pointless ideas.

384
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:20,710
Who is it?

385
00:19:21,140 --> 00:19:22,340
Who is it?

386
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:23,060
I'm coming.

387
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:24,950
Be good while eating.

388
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:26,340
I'm coming.

389
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:31,990
Mrs. Wan.

390
00:19:32,820 --> 00:19:34,820
We're here to see Mr. Wan.

391
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:37,670
Dad.

392
00:19:38,140 --> 00:19:40,270
Qinglai is here with his wife,
whom he just married.

393
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,670
You two are here.

394
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,190
Mr. Wan.

395
00:19:54,190 --> 00:19:55,470
You're...

396
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:56,100
Chuanjia.

397
00:19:56,580 --> 00:19:57,300
Well...

398
00:19:57,780 --> 00:19:58,580
Mr. Wan.

399
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:01,300
I brought Xingfu

400
00:20:01,910 --> 00:20:03,300
with me here today

401
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:04,470
to send our apologies.

402
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:07,470
Xingfu didn't think it through

403
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,300
when she hit you yesterday.

404
00:20:09,670 --> 00:20:10,910
It was a stupid mistake.

405
00:20:10,910 --> 00:20:11,710
You...

406
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:12,580
Can you be

407
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:14,380
the bigger person

408
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:16,430
and forgive us this time?

409
00:20:21,380 --> 00:20:22,340
Qinglai.

410
00:20:23,230 --> 00:20:25,060
You weren't the one who hit me yesterday.

411
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:27,620
Why are you doing all the talking?

412
00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:28,950
Moreover,

413
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:30,380
why weren't you there yesterday

414
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:31,540
to keep your wife under control?

415
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:38,380
Mr. Wan.

416
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,710
Chuanjia.

417
00:20:40,190 --> 00:20:41,860
It was my fault that I hit you yesterday.

418
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:43,860
I apologize to you.

419
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,510
That's enough.

420
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:47,340
It's very good to see that Xingfu is remorseful

421
00:20:47,340 --> 00:20:48,030
for her mistake.

422
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:49,910
Let's end this matter here.

423
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:50,950
But...

424
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:52,300
There are still a few words I need to tell you.

425
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:53,230
Xingfu.

426
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:54,620
The Wan Village

427
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:56,270
is unlike the other villages.

428
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:57,470
Our motto is,

429
00:20:57,470 --> 00:20:58,620
"All for Wan,

430
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:00,100
Wan for All."

431
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:00,710
Get it?

432
00:21:00,710 --> 00:21:01,580
We can only prosper

433
00:21:01,580 --> 00:21:02,430
if all the members of the village

434
00:21:02,430 --> 00:21:03,470
can work together harmoniously.

435
00:21:03,820 --> 00:21:04,510
Don't you agree?

436
00:21:04,510 --> 00:21:06,430
Xingfu only did that yesterday

437
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:08,190
because she was feeling giddy.

438
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:11,670
She spent an entire night
regretting what she did.

439
00:21:12,300 --> 00:21:13,270
Don't worry.

440
00:21:13,380 --> 00:21:14,470
This time,

441
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:15,620
she'll surely learn her lesson.

442
00:21:16,670 --> 00:21:18,190
An entire night?

443
00:21:18,470 --> 00:21:20,300
Then, did you have the time
for the main event last night?

444
00:21:22,860 --> 00:21:24,670
You're the senior.
How could you say things like that?

445
00:21:28,540 --> 00:21:29,140
Alright.

446
00:21:29,470 --> 00:21:30,950
It's not a big deal.

447
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:32,580
Let's put it behind us

448
00:21:33,190 --> 00:21:33,990
and carry on with our lives.

449
00:21:34,990 --> 00:21:35,820
Thanks, Mr. Wan.

450
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,580
It's fine.

451
00:21:36,580 --> 00:21:38,780
My dad told me to bring you these.

452
00:21:38,780 --> 00:21:40,140
I'll leave them here.

453
00:21:40,540 --> 00:21:42,030
That's too kind of you.

454
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:43,990
We'll get going.

455
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:44,670
Sure.

456
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:45,750
Chuanjia, see them out.

457
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:46,750
Let's go, Xingfu.

458
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:47,820
Wait a minute.

459
00:21:48,990 --> 00:21:50,100
I'm not done yet.

460
00:21:52,470 --> 00:21:53,510
Mr. Wan.

461
00:21:53,780 --> 00:21:55,140
It was my fault that I assaulted him.

462
00:21:56,030 --> 00:21:57,470
I brought you gifts
and apologized for my mistake.

463
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:01,060
Then, what about the things

464
00:22:02,300 --> 00:22:03,620
Chuanjia did to my sister?

465
00:22:06,820 --> 00:22:08,300
Xingfu, what are you talking about?

466
00:22:08,430 --> 00:22:10,270
What is this?

467
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:12,270
Let's go.

468
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:14,030
He owes my sister an explanation.

469
00:22:14,190 --> 00:22:14,950
Mr. Wan.

470
00:22:15,430 --> 00:22:16,780
I only hit Chuanjia

471
00:22:16,780 --> 00:22:18,540
because he bullied my sister.

472
00:22:18,820 --> 00:22:20,510
Let's talk things out.

473
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,140
I didn't bully your sister, all right?

474
00:22:22,580 --> 00:22:24,230
You got married, right?

475
00:22:24,230 --> 00:22:25,380
I was just having fun at the wedding.

476
00:22:25,380 --> 00:22:27,230
We were all having fun and it was just a joke.

477
00:22:27,230 --> 00:22:28,820
We were all trying to create a good atmosphere.

478
00:22:28,820 --> 00:22:30,990
-It was just a joke.
-You bullied her.

479
00:22:30,990 --> 00:22:32,270
Xingfu.

480
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:33,910
A wedding day is a happy day.

481
00:22:33,910 --> 00:22:35,230
We all want to make it fun.

482
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,380
As the old saying says,

483
00:22:37,030 --> 00:22:38,670
"There are no rules during the first three days
of the marriage."

484
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:39,860
Although

485
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:41,710
the joke was a little too much,

486
00:22:41,820 --> 00:22:43,060
it's not unforgivable.

487
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:44,820
But that was too much, Mr. Wan.

488
00:22:45,710 --> 00:22:47,470
My younger sister just graduated from college.

489
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:48,620
She is still single.

490
00:22:48,910 --> 00:22:50,540
How is she supposed to live with this?

491
00:22:50,540 --> 00:22:51,820
I understand, but...

492
00:22:51,820 --> 00:22:53,380
What do you want then?

493
00:22:53,990 --> 00:22:54,910
Mr. Wan.

494
00:22:54,910 --> 00:22:56,820
I suppose you're a sensible man.

495
00:22:57,510 --> 00:22:58,910
It was my fault that I hit him,

496
00:22:59,270 --> 00:23:01,100
but Chuanjia is at fault too
for what he did to my sister.

497
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:03,670
Qinglai.

498
00:23:03,670 --> 00:23:05,100
How often do you pay respects

499
00:23:05,100 --> 00:23:07,060
to your ancestors

500
00:23:07,060 --> 00:23:08,510
to get such a wife?

