00:31:33,620 --> 00:31:34,990
Don't keep things to yourself.

747
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:35,780
Just say it.

748
00:31:36,580 --> 00:31:37,990
Get up.

749
00:31:42,510 --> 00:31:43,380
Why don't we

750
00:31:43,950 --> 00:31:45,430
go to Mr. Wan's place

751
00:31:45,430 --> 00:31:46,510
and apologize to him again tomorrow?

752
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:49,100
What?

753
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:51,580
Why should I apologize to him again?

754
00:31:52,430 --> 00:31:53,820
Did I do something wrong again?

755
00:31:54,190 --> 00:31:55,340
All this would have been over now

756
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,670
with an apology from you.

757
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:59,270
Yet you insisted on
having Chuanjia apologize to your sister.

758
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:01,270
And you even pulled a long face before Mr. Wan.

759
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,540
Now that you've driven him mad,

760
00:32:02,540 --> 00:32:04,190
how are you...

761
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:06,670
You think it's right for Wan Chuanjia

762
00:32:06,670 --> 00:32:07,540
to have bullied my sister?

763
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:10,580
And Mr. Wan was mean to me because of this.

764
00:32:11,710 --> 00:32:13,780
In fact, I feel wronged.

765
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:14,990
As my husband,

766
00:32:14,990 --> 00:32:16,580
you dared not defend me

767
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:18,060
when he was being mean to me.

768
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:21,140
And you have the cheek
to ask me to apologize to him.

769
00:32:21,670 --> 00:32:23,140
How could you even suggest that?

770
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:24,140
But

771
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:25,910
you messed with the secretary.

772
00:32:25,910 --> 00:32:27,300
How are we going to make a living here?

773
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:28,620
Nothing will change.

774
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:29,670
We just live our lives as they are.

775
00:32:29,670 --> 00:32:31,030
I don't believe he can do anything to me!

776
00:32:32,140 --> 00:32:32,950
I'm telling you.

777
00:32:32,950 --> 00:32:34,340
If he's really not going to say sorry,

778
00:32:34,340 --> 00:32:35,710
I won't let this slide!

779
00:32:36,540 --> 00:32:37,230
Go to sleep!

780
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:50,230
Guizhi.

781
00:32:50,230 --> 00:32:51,620
Do you think

782
00:32:52,340 --> 00:32:53,190
Mr. Wan

783
00:32:53,190 --> 00:32:54,510
will fight

784
00:32:54,750 --> 00:32:55,710
with some lass who is new in the village?

785
00:32:56,030 --> 00:32:56,670
He will.

786
00:32:57,540 --> 00:32:59,470
Mr. Wan is a man of principle.

787
00:33:01,190 --> 00:33:02,750
Well, our family is dead meat.

788
00:33:03,230 --> 00:33:04,620
We messed with Mr. Wan.

789
00:33:22,100 --> 00:33:22,990
How about this?

790
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:24,510
We will visit

791
00:33:25,340 --> 00:33:26,510
Mr. Wan again tomorrow.

792
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:27,910
And apologize to him again.

793
00:33:28,670 --> 00:33:29,620
Well, in my opinion,

794
00:33:29,620 --> 00:33:31,820
there's nothing bad
about Xingfu's hotheadedness.

795
00:33:32,340 --> 00:33:33,780
Back then, our family

796
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:35,780
would always be tolerant and give in to things.

797
00:33:35,780 --> 00:33:38,300
Now that we've got an explosive daughter-in-law,

798
00:33:38,910 --> 00:33:40,380
people will think twice

799
00:33:40,670 --> 00:33:42,100
before they mess with us.

800
00:33:42,510 --> 00:33:44,470
Well, aren't you worried

801
00:33:44,470 --> 00:33:46,140
that she will become
more and more temperamental?

802
00:33:46,580 --> 00:33:47,950
What if she ends up

803
00:33:47,950 --> 00:33:48,620
being out of control?

804
00:33:49,030 --> 00:33:50,060
As the saying goes,

805
00:33:50,060 --> 00:33:52,230
time leads one to the ways of the world.

806
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:54,580
She may be young and wild now.

807
00:33:54,580 --> 00:33:55,620
But once she's given birth

808
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:56,820
after some time,

809
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:58,780
she will know how to behave herself.

810
00:34:01,670 --> 00:34:03,300
But how do we deal with Mr. Wan?

811
00:34:14,230 --> 00:34:15,580
Looks like Mr. Wan is not around.

812
00:34:18,660 --> 00:34:19,740
He's off to a meeting?

813
00:34:19,740 --> 00:34:20,390
Perhaps.

814
00:34:24,430 --> 00:34:25,700
Mrs. Wan, is Mr. Wan...

815
00:34:25,700 --> 00:34:27,790
My dad is occupied. You should leave.

816
00:34:28,180 --> 00:34:28,790
Don't...

817
00:34:31,510 --> 00:34:32,100
Why don't we

818
00:34:32,540 --> 00:34:33,870
kneel before him again?

819
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:36,100
How dare you do that again?

820
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:37,390
Have you forgotten what happened the other day?

821
00:34:39,030 --> 00:34:41,140
How about this? Let Mr. Wan cool off first.

822
00:34:41,140 --> 00:34:42,740
And we will visit him

823
00:34:42,740 --> 00:34:44,260
and apologize to him another day.

824
00:34:44,260 --> 00:34:45,700
What about Xingfu?

825
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:47,260
She's relentless.

826
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:48,580
And we didn't manage to placate Mr. Wan.

827
00:34:48,580 --> 00:34:49,990
We're basically stuck in the middle.

828
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,910
I'm thinking...

829
00:34:58,310 --> 00:34:59,390
That won't do.

830
00:34:59,390 --> 00:35:00,260
Why not?

831
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:02,060
We're going to use my money, not yours.

832
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:03,140
Where did your money come from?

833
00:35:03,140 --> 00:35:04,350
I gave it to you.

834
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:06,870
All you care about is money.

835
00:35:07,580 --> 00:35:09,470
Fine, since you're full of ideas, you settle it.
I'll stay out of it.

836
00:35:09,470 --> 00:35:11,910
No, but the thing
is that we're not going to get it back.

837
00:35:17,390 --> 00:35:19,100
Come here, Xingfu.

838
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:20,790
I have something to tell you.

839
00:35:22,740 --> 00:35:23,620
-What is it?
-Take a seat.

840
00:35:25,910 --> 00:35:26,580
Look.

841
00:35:27,990 --> 00:35:29,390
Here's 1,000 yuan

842
00:35:29,390 --> 00:35:31,140
from Mr. Wan to you.

843
00:35:32,220 --> 00:35:33,350
It's from Mr. Wan?

844
00:35:33,990 --> 00:35:35,390
Did you go to see him again?

845
00:35:35,470 --> 00:35:37,870
Well, your dad and Mr. Wan

846
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:39,580
have been working together for years.

847
00:35:39,580 --> 00:35:40,870
They go way back.

848
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:43,430
It's only right for him to have shown
your dad some respect.

849
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:48,030
Why did he give me this money?

850
00:35:48,030 --> 00:35:49,220
He said...

851
00:35:49,220 --> 00:35:51,390
Well, he had a fit of anger yesterday.

852
00:35:51,390 --> 00:35:53,310
But, when he got home, he gave it a good thought.

853
00:35:53,310 --> 00:35:55,910
And it's not right for Chuanjia
to have bullied your sister.

854
00:35:56,220 --> 00:35:58,390
He even told Chuanjia

855
00:35:58,390 --> 00:36:00,350
to serve both of us tea.

856
00:36:00,350 --> 00:36:02,220
And he apologized to us

857
00:36:02,220 --> 00:36:03,390
for what happened to your sister.

858
00:36:03,790 --> 00:36:05,830
He said this was a token of apology from him.

859
00:36:14,430 --> 00:36:14,990
Dad.

860
00:36:15,470 --> 00:36:16,990
Did Wan Chuanjia admit his fault?

861
00:36:19,310 --> 00:36:19,830
Yeah.

862
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:21,350
He did.

863
00:36:21,430 --> 00:36:22,220
You see,

864
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:24,540
now that both our families have talked it out,

865
00:36:24,870 --> 00:36:26,910
it's water under the bridge now.

866
00:36:27,620 --> 00:36:29,220
Besides, Mr. Wan said

867
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:31,910
that he likes your personality.

868
00:36:31,910 --> 00:36:34,470
That Qinglai has gotten himself a good wife.

869
00:36:35,260 --> 00:36:36,830
I don't need him to like me.

870
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,390
I just want Wan Chuanjia

871
00:36:38,390 --> 00:36:39,910
to apologize to my sister.

872
00:36:40,830 --> 00:36:42,660
What's this money for?

873
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:45,310
You stubborn girl.

874
00:36:45,310 --> 00:36:46,580
You're not happy with anything.

875
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:48,510
Can't you just let it slide?

876
00:36:48,510 --> 00:36:50,390
Indeed. We said,

877
00:36:50,390 --> 00:36:51,350
"We don't want the money.

878
00:36:51,470 --> 00:36:52,950
There's no way we're accepting it."

879
00:36:53,220 --> 00:36:54,910
Mr. Wan got upset hearing that.

880
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:56,580
Anyway,

881
00:36:57,260 --> 00:36:58,660
it's a token of apology from him.

882
00:36:58,660 --> 00:36:59,700
Right, Xingfu?

883
00:37:00,220 --> 00:37:01,260
There's no way

884
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:03,350
you should reject an elder like him, right?

885
00:37:07,390 --> 00:37:09,030
Well, that's settled.

886
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,700
Mr. Wan said,

887
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:12,540
"This is the end of it."

888
00:37:12,660 --> 00:37:14,620
It's great to have turned the page.

889
00:37:14,740 --> 00:37:15,310
Isn't it?

890
00:37:15,310 --> 00:37:16,260
From now on,

891
00:37:16,350 --> 00:37:18,220
we will live our lives honestly.

892
00:37:18,220 --> 00:37:18,950
We will all be fine.

893
00:37:18,950 --> 00:37:19,580
It's in the past.

894
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:21,470
No one is going to bring it up again.

895
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:23,140
It's all over now.

896
00:37:41,430 --> 00:37:42,540
Are you making dried eggplant, Xingfu?

897
00:37:42,950 --> 00:37:45,310
Braised meat with dried eggplant
is my favorite dish.

898
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:47,910
Xingfu?

899
00:37:49,740 --> 00:37:50,870
What's the matter with you, Xingfu?

900
00:37:50,870 --> 00:37:51,660
I'm fine.

901
00:37:53,100 --> 00:37:53,990
Qingzhi.

902
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:55,140
You came just in time. Come here.

903
00:37:56,740 --> 00:37:57,700
I'm troubled

904
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:59,060
by something.

905
00:37:59,350 --> 00:38:00,350
You're a postgraduate student.

906
00:38:00,350 --> 00:38:01,100
That makes you cultured.

907
00:38:01,390 --> 00:38:02,660
Help me to get my head around it.

908
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:04,180
Go ahead, Xingfu.

909
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:06,350
Dad and Mom said

910
00:38:06,350 --> 00:38:08,140
that they went to see Mr. Wan again.

911
00:38:08,790 --> 00:38:10,700
That Mr. Wan had Wan Chuanjia

912
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:12,950
apologize to my sister in front of our parents.

913
00:38:13,310 --> 00:38:14,830
And he even gave me 1,000 yuan.

914
00:38:16,470 --> 00:38:17,830
That's new to me.

915
00:38:18,470 --> 00:38:19,310
Right?

916
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:21,310
Well, do you think

917
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:23,830
I should accept the money?

918
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:27,180
Logically speaking,

919
00:38:27,180 --> 00:38:28,830
since Xingyun was bullied by Chuanjia,

920
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:30,350
it's reasonable

921
00:38:30,350 --> 00:38:31,870
for Mr. Wan to have given you

922
00:38:32,060 --> 00:38:33,180
the money as compensation.

923
00:38:33,990 --> 00:38:35,310
It's just that...

924
00:38:36,220 --> 00:38:37,030
What?

925
00:38:37,620 --> 00:38:39,140
This is just my personal opinion, Xingfu.

926
00:38:40,060 --> 00:38:41,350
It's just

927
00:38:41,470 --> 00:38:43,740
that the situation has changed

928
00:38:43,740 --> 00:38:45,390
with Mr. Wan giving you this money.

929
00:38:45,950 --> 00:38:46,700
It's as if

930
00:38:47,310 --> 00:38:49,510
you asked them for an apology

931
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:51,180
because you were after this 1,000 yuan.

932
00:38:51,390 --> 00:38:53,620
That's what I thought, Qingzhi.

933
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:55,220
All I've been after

934
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:56,700
is nothing but an explanation from them.

935
00:38:57,180 --> 00:38:58,430
If we are to talk about compensation,

936
00:38:58,830 --> 00:39:00,700
I injured Wan Chuanjia's head,

937
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:01,700
so logically speaking,

938
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:03,220
I should pay his medical bill.

939
00:39:03,350 --> 00:39:04,700
But he's not asking me to do so.

940
00:39:05,030 --> 00:39:05,660
Yeah.

941
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:08,830
This won't do.

942
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:10,990
I have to return this money to Mr. Wan.

943
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:14,620
Thank you, Qingzhi.

944
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:32,140
I'm going to beat you up, brat!

945
00:39:32,310 --> 00:39:33,540
Let's talk it out, Dad!

946
00:39:33,540 --> 00:39:34,100
Why are you hitting me?

947
00:39:34,100 --> 00:39:35,260
Talk it out?

948
00:39:36,430 --> 00:39:37,510
You're driving me mad!

949
00:39:37,950 --> 00:39:39,140
Just because you're an intellectual?

950
00:39:39,390 --> 00:39:40,430
What did you mean by that?

951
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:41,830
Hurry up, go after her!

952
00:39:41,830 --> 00:39:42,910
The situation has changed
with the money involved?

953
00:39:42,910 --> 00:39:44,790
That was truly a bad idea, Mom.

954
00:39:44,790 --> 00:39:46,540
I knew Xingfu wouldn't accept the money.

955
00:39:46,540 --> 00:39:48,060
What's the use of saying that now?

956
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:50,390
Quick! If she manages to see Mr. Wan, we'll be done for!

957
00:39:50,390 --> 00:39:50,990
Hurry up!

958
00:39:50,990 --> 00:39:52,260
Quick! You must stop her!

959
00:39:52,260 --> 00:39:54,430
If she sees Mr. Wan, we will be in trouble!

960
00:39:54,430 --> 00:39:55,390
Mom. Dad.

961
00:39:55,390 --> 00:39:57,580
Well, you shouldn't have lied to Xingfu.

962
00:39:58,790 --> 00:39:59,740
Oh, no!

963
00:39:59,740 --> 00:40:00,510
I'm going to teach you a lesson.

964
00:40:01,430 --> 00:40:03,260
What are you doing?

965
00:40:03,790 --> 00:40:05,060
You think I wanted to do that?

966
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:07,510
My 1,000 yuan is gone for nothing.

967
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:08,700
And I'm still distressed by it!

968
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:10,350
What can I do since your brother married

969
00:40:10,350 --> 00:40:11,910
such an unreasonable wife?

970
00:40:11,910 --> 00:40:14,310
I thought of solving the problem with that money.

971
00:40:14,310 --> 00:40:15,310
And now?

972
00:40:15,310 --> 00:40:16,740
The money is gone, and we're in deep water!

973
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:20,660
It's all your fault
for coming up with that bad idea.

974
00:40:20,660 --> 00:40:22,180
Why didn't you give her 2,000 yuan instead?

975
00:40:29,390 --> 00:40:29,990
Mom.

976
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:32,950
I'm okay, Mom. He didn't hit me.

977
00:40:41,223 --> 00:40:42,830
[Village Branch Committee of Wan Village]

978
00:40:42,830 --> 00:40:43,430
Cailiang.

979
00:40:43,790 --> 00:40:45,100
It's still early, don't head home yet.

980
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:45,740
Come with me to the Wanjia Group.

981
00:40:45,740 --> 00:40:46,430
Are you heading out, Mr. Wan?

982
00:40:47,220 --> 00:40:48,180
Okay, sure.

983
00:40:48,180 --> 00:40:49,030
Mr. Wan!

984
00:40:49,310 --> 00:40:50,510
Hold up, Mr. Wan.

985
00:40:50,910 --> 00:40:52,260
It's you again. What is it?

986
00:40:52,740 --> 00:40:53,430
Mr. Wan.

987
00:40:53,740 --> 00:40:54,830
Since Chuanjia has apologized to my sister...

